  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-commodity\">supremely powerful</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Humboldt Drive</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Potential improvements include: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">acceleration</span>, <span class=\"name name-stellar\">fuel efficiency</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">top speed</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">洪堡驱动器</span>的至强<span class=\"name name-commodity\"><>提升。使用<VAL_ON><IMG>FE_ALT1</span><>开始<VAL_ON>安装升级<>。<br><br>该模块很灵活，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">加速</span>、<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃料效率</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">最高速度</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">洪堡驱动器</span>的一个<span class=\"name name-commodity\">至强</span>提升。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>开始安装升级。<br><br>可极大地提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">加速</span>、<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃料效率</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">最高速度</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-commodity\">洪保德驅動器</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">最強大</span>升級。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組富有彈性，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能強化的項目包括：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">加速</span>、<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃料效率</span>及<span class=\"name name-stellar\">最高速度</span>。"
  },
